    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This basic Kendo-style attack targets the throat in order to deal a stunning blow that can cause great pain to the foe.<br><br>The user must be wielding a Kendo Stick in order to perform this technique. The user makes an attack roll at a -2 penalty specifically targeting the throat. The attack deals normal weapon damage and causes the target to become stunned for 1 round.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Material Focus:</b> The user's hel d Kendo Stick.</p>\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> At fifth level of mastery, the target becomes stunned for 1d4+1 rounds (instead of 1).</p>\n",
